Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: DP: Add support to collect and
 prepare SDWF stats

Add support to determine the buffer size required to send SDWF
statistics. Also add logic to collect SDWF TX and delay statistics
based on the configured parameters.

